Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.68,0:02:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼蕾之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於到達煌珠樂園的酷他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.41,0:02:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有著和人類社會一樣的生活過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.99,0:02:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家各自奮戰之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.65,0:02:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使在寶座之上的蕾加冕為女王的儀式開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.86,0:02:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷雖然逼近至咫尺之遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.20,0:02:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但受到出現在眼前的ChaosChoir的幹部們的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.35,0:02:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其生命之線不費吹灰之力就被剪斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.65,0:02:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經沒有誰能救蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.73,0:02:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此下去ChaosChoir得以統治人類了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.64,0:03:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十五唱 ChaosChoir
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.58,0:03:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,礙事的同契者已經收拾掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.22,0:03:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一來那孩子就完完全全屬於我們的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.77,0:03:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舉行蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯大人加冕為女王的儀式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.00,0:04:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.64,0:04:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在煌珠樂園的周圍戰鬥好像還在繼續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.60,0:04:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是男人的話就要說到做到啊 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在磨磨蹭蹭地幹什麼 酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.10,0:04:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點結束這戰爭 酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.16,0:04:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.49,0:04:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前 前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.50,0:04:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是酷和蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定能喚醒失去的頌詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下去怎麼辦 希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.74,0:05:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.39,0:05:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去追那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.64,0:05:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救出蕾 制止戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.91,0:05:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.11,0:05:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷也肯定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.43,0:05:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼希望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.31,0:06:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你加冕為煌珠樂園的女王的時刻終於到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.09,0:06:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭恭敬敬{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賀祝皇位繼承{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尊者無需開口{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.91,0:06:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玉裳加身{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祝頌七煌寶樹{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,風雅端莊{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯有汝{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.92,0:06:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彼等所依唯有公主{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.27,0:06:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此刻請登基{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.83,0:06:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼承大統{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千秋萬代歌頌{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡天喜地{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誠心誠意{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.46,0:06:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敬奉上天{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.74,0:07:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祭祀上蒼之謬{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.01,0:07:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必得贖罪{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.44,0:07:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,純潔之白{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.19,0:07:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神靈之弓{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.83,0:07:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,深藏在心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.00,0:07:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此 一切準備就緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.41,0:07:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓蕾做女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們有什麼目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.95,0:07:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能得到七煌寶樹的強大力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.18,0:07:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擊潰守護翼就易如反掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不僅如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.81,0:07:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還能把妨礙我們的人全部幹掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.37,0:07:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護翼已經決定停止攻擊煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.43,0:08:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以也請你們別再戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.52,0:08:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己打過來的就別隨便命令別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是再這樣打下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.40,0:08:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護者 擬煌珠 以及煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.14,0:08:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多很多的人都將受到傷害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.41,0:08:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把煌珠當作道具使其受傷的不是守護者嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.57,0:08:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確 我們是錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.91,0:08:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 正因為這樣才不想爭戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.53,0:08:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.82,0:08:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠和人類曾共同歌頌 創造奇跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在也只要煌珠和人類同心協力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平共處是可以做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.05,0:08:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只追求戰鬥的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.43,0:08:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘掉創造奇跡的頌詞的是守護者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.79,0:08:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在有能唱頌那頌詞的守護者嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.43,0:08:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和你們攜手是毫無必要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.40,0:09:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煌珠樂園的女王——蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯大人的強大力量
