Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽吾之禱{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.60,0:09:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,懲罰這人心不古的世界{\a6}
