Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.20,0:09:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒趕上嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.48,0:10:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯大人的強大力量現在已是我們的了
